## GitHub Actions Runner Environment
## Secrets injected by Ansible from Bitwarden at deploy time.

## GitHub App auth — both read from /run/secrets/ at container start.
## No secrets in this file.

## DockerHub
DOCKERHUB_USERNAME=amerenda

## Runner config
RUNNER_SCOPE=repo
## EPHEMERAL=true  # Disabled — ephemeral runners miss queued jobs during restart cycle
RUNNER_WORKDIR=/_work
RANDOM_RUNNER_SUFFIX=false
